    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GreenBulb 是一款有趣且充满色彩的单人跳跃游戏，在20个关卡中，你将通过解谜和技能测试来挑战自己的反应与灵活度。GreenBulb拥有独特的能力，可以通过踢或跳跃来“转换”形状。如果能够在不触地的情况下连续转换多个形状，将获得更高的分数。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094610/extras/bdb16c8660374cab3c558780c7d860b5.avif?t=1729077949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094610/extras_big/bdb16c8660374cab3c558780c7d860b5.avif?t=1729077949 width=800 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GreenBulb必须对抗Shape Machine，这是一台可怕的复制设备，它不断释放出无意义的重复形状。只有GreenBulb能够拯救世界，将这些毫无生机的形状变成色彩斑斓且令人愉悦的物体！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094610/extras/5121d2c0fca2c76a0722779432bae89f.avif?t=1729077949\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3094610/extras_big/5121d2c0fca2c76a0722779432bae89f.avif?t=1729077949 width=800 height=262 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：1-8关是免费的，提供了有趣而富有挑战性的体验。要解锁8关以后的关卡，玩家可以支付2.99美元一次性购买“解锁所有关卡”道具，从而顺利通关，最终挑战Boss关卡。</strong></p>",
